      "id": "featured-text",
      "type": "text",
      "data": {
        "content": "<p>As we step into 2025, email marketing continues to evolve at an unprecedented pace. Artificial intelligence, hyper-personalization, and privacy-first strategies are reshaping how brands connect with their audiences.</p><p>In this comprehensive analysis, we explore the key trends that will define email marketing success this year. From interactive AMP emails to zero-party data collection, discover the strategies that leading brands are already implementing to stay ahead of the curve.</p><p>We'll also dive into the challenges marketers face with Apple's Mail Privacy Protection and iOS updates, and share actionable tactics to maintain high deliverability rates while respecting subscriber privacy. Whether you're a seasoned email marketer or just getting started, these insights will help you build more effective campaigns in 2025.</p>",
        "fontFamily": "-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif",
        "fontSize": "16px",
        "color": "#4B5563",
        "lineHeight": 1.6
